{
  "title": "🔬 Lab: Anti-Pattern vs Gauge Fix — Side by Side",
  "uid": "airflow-lab-comparison",
  "tags": ["airflow", "lab", "comparison"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "dag_id",
        "label": "DAG",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(airflow_dag_run_duration_seconds, dag_id)",
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## 🔬 Interactive Lab: The Pushgateway Race Condition\nThis dashboard compares **V1 Anti-Pattern (Counters)** vs **V2 Gauge Fix (Gauges)** side by side.\n\n**How to run the simulation:**\n1. Set `AIRFLOW_VAR_ENABLE_V1_COUNTERS=true`, trigger `race_condition_simulator` → watch V1 show **1** failure\n2. Set `AIRFLOW_VAR_ENABLE_V2_GAUGES=true`, trigger again → watch V2 correctly show **10** failures"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "❌ V1: Anti-Pattern — Counter-based (Broken)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "V1 — Task Failures Recorded",
      "description": "Uses Counter. With 10 simultaneous failures, this will show 1 due to the race condition.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (dag_id) (max_over_time(airflow_task_instance_failures_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"}[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{dag_id}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "V1 — Tasks Running",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (dag_id) (max_over_time(airflow_task_instance_state_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", state=\"running\"}[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{dag_id}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "blue", "value": null }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "V1 — Tasks Succeeded",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (dag_id) (max_over_time(airflow_task_instance_state_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\", state=\"success\"}[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{dag_id}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "V1 — Task Failure Types",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (type) (max_over_time(airflow_task_instance_failures_by_type_total{job=\"airflow_tasks\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"}[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "pieType": "donut", "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true } }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "✅ V2: Gauge Fix — State Snapshots (Correct)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 11, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "V2 — Task Failures Recorded",
      "description": "Uses Gauge + count(). With 10 simultaneous failures, this correctly shows 10.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(airflow_task_instance_status{job=\"airflow_tasks_v2\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} == -1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Failed Tasks",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "V2 — Tasks Running",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 12, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(airflow_task_instance_status{job=\"airflow_tasks_v2\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} == 0) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Running Tasks",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "blue", "value": null }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "V2 — Tasks Succeeded",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 12, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(airflow_task_instance_status{job=\"airflow_tasks_v2\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} == 1) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "Successful Tasks",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "V2 — Task Failure Types",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 12, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count by (type) (airflow_task_instance_failure_type{job=\"airflow_tasks_v2\", dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} == 1)",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": { "pieType": "donut", "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true } }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "📊 Shared: Duration Metrics (work for both V1 and V2)",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 24, "h": 1 },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "DAG Duration Per Run",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "airflow_dag_run_duration_seconds{dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} unless (airflow_dag_run_duration_seconds{dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} offset 2m)",
          "legendFormat": "{{dag_id}} — {{run_id}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "custom": { "drawStyle": "points", "pointSize": 8 } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Task Duration Per Run",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "Prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "airflow_task_instance_duration_seconds{dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} unless (airflow_task_instance_duration_seconds{dag_id=~\"$dag_id\"} offset 2m)",
          "legendFormat": "{{task_id}} — {{run_id}}",
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "custom": { "drawStyle": "points", "pointSize": 8 } } }
    }
  ]
}